description:
The investment seeks to provide investment results that, before fees and expenses, track the total return performance of the Toroso ETF Industry Index.
 The fund normally invests at least 80% of its total assets in securities of the index. The index is designed to measure the performance of an investable universe of publicly-traded companies that directly or indirectly provide services or support to exchange-traded funds ("ETFs"), including but not limited to the management, servicing, trading or sale of ETFs ("ETF Activities"), as determined by Toroso Investments, LLC (the "index provider"). The fund is non-diversified.
